      "description": "CFD velocity fields compared against FDA-published PIV measurements for the generic centrifugal blood pump geometry. Agreement within 12% RMS across the impeller passage at design-point flow rate (6 L/min, 3500 RPM). Provides geometric and flow-regime relevance to VAD operating envelope."
